sequenceDiagram
  actor U as User
  participant T as Tool (static)
  participant F as Pages Function
  participant K as KV

  U->>T: open /mermaid/
  T->>F: GET /api/assets
  F->>K: list prefix user:
  K-->>F: [slugs + metadata]
  F-->>T: my diagrams
  U->>T: Save
  T->>F: PUT /api/assets/:slug
  F->>K: put user:slug
  F-->>T: { ok: true }
